32:18.948 --> 32:20.368
I-I couldn't sleep.

32:21.075 --> 32:22.344
It's beautiful.

32:23.287 --> 32:24.615
Is it about Scarlett?

32:25.190 --> 32:26.783
I guess.

32:26.784 --> 32:28.022
Maybe.

32:36.750 --> 32:38.119
You think she's gonna be okay?

32:39.108 --> 32:40.386
I don't know.

