- Morning.
- Hey.

33:26.169 --> 33:28.404
Sorry. Guess I fell asleep.

33:34.137 --> 33:37.225
The last few days have
been kind of rough, huh?

33:38.421 --> 33:40.440
That is the understatement of the year.

33:41.541 --> 33:42.844
How you feeling?

33:45.533 --> 33:46.759
Not really sure yet.

33:51.481 --> 33:52.853
What are you doing here?

33:54.247 --> 33:57.648
You wouldn't let go of
my hand when it happened.

33:59.541 --> 34:02.005
I know how you feel about Beverly, and...

34:03.334 --> 34:04.757
I know you.

34:04.758 --> 34:06.455
And I just figured a friendly face

34:06.456 --> 34:07.984
wouldn't be a bad thing.

34:09.893 --> 34:11.266
It's not.

34:13.527 --> 34:15.639
Thank you for always being there for me.

34:17.908 --> 34:19.606
You were my first love.

34:21.114 --> 34:22.493
You know that?

34:23.532 --> 34:26.382
I don't think I'll ever love
anyone as much as I loved you.

34:28.255 --> 34:31.152
I don't want anything bad to happen to you.

34:31.154 --> 34:32.460
You hear me?

34:33.346 --> 34:36.541
You got a permanent piece
of my heart, Scarlett.

34:38.283 --> 34:39.855
Always will.

34:56.734 --> 34:58.816
Hey.

34:58.817 --> 35:00.333
Clean bill of health from the doctors, huh?

35:01.067 --> 35:03.660
Well, yeah. I already knew
I wasn't a drug addict.

35:03.661 --> 35:04.871
So did I.

35:06.399 --> 35:07.923
When can I go back out?

35:10.476 --> 35:12.857
I think you been spending a lot of time

35:12.858 --> 35:14.801
<i>worrying about what's gonna make me happy.</i>

35:16.134 --> 35:17.680
Now's the time for you to think about

35:17.681 --> 35:19.332
<i>what's gonna make you happy.</i>

35:21.067 --> 35:23.386
I'm gonna ask you a question
that I asked you before.

35:24.394 --> 35:26.056
I want you to answer me honestly.

35:29.352 --> 35:30.642
Do you want this?

35:34.721 --> 35:36.237
No, I don't.

35:38.811 --> 35:40.601
I don't know what I want, but...

35:42.691 --> 35:44.136
I don't want this.

35:45.141 --> 35:48.110
Feel like you've been trying
to tell me that for a while.

35:49.084 --> 35:50.838
Sorry I wasted your time.

35:50.839 --> 35:53.298
<i>Hey, listen, you figured out
something you don't want to do.</i>

35:53.299 --> 35:54.583
I mean, that is every bit as important

35:54.584 --> 35:56.352
<i>as figuring out what you do want to do.</i>

35:57.042 --> 35:58.903
You've got a great future ahead of you.

35:59.676 --> 36:02.096
It's just gonna mean going
down a different road.

36:04.441 --> 36:06.364
I'm gonna release you from your contract.

36:18.079 --> 36:21.144
Whoa! Haven't seen the girls
out like that in a while.

36:21.664 --> 36:23.922
Know what... I'm allowed to get dressed up

36:23.923 --> 36:25.730
and go out whenever I want to.

36:26.112 --> 36:27.482
I was just kidding.

36:27.846 --> 36:30.053
The car's gonna be here
pretty soon. Where's Avery?

36:30.655 --> 36:33.806
Avery is... Too busy
with his ex-girlfriend

36:33.807 --> 36:35.871
to be concerned about his current one.

36:35.872 --> 36:38.257
Well... I'll come with you. It'll be fun.

36:38.258 --> 36:41.926
No. I don't need a pity
date or a babysitter, okay?

36:41.927 --> 36:43.326
I'm going alone.

36:47.312 --> 36:48.484
You wanted me?

36:48.908 --> 36:49.948
Yeah.

36:50.869 --> 36:52.137
I need you to drive me home.

36:53.054 --> 36:54.241
Oh.

36:56.338 --> 36:57.972
No more pills, right?

36:58.819 --> 37:00.270
<i>What do you reckon?</i>

37:04.328 --> 37:05.506
Okay.

37:06.050 --> 37:07.164
Hey.

37:08.441 --> 37:09.622
What are you doing?

37:10.030 --> 37:12.867
I'm, uh... I'm signing myself out.

37:12.868 --> 37:15.655
