39:50.389 --> 39:52.089
I don't want to be a star.

39:52.502 --> 39:54.509
♪ Think of all the morning
stars you would've missed ♪

39:54.510 --> 39:56.116
I told Zoey I didn't know how I got there,

39:56.117 --> 39:59.197
but... I do.

39:59.198 --> 40:00.471
I...

40:01.604 --> 40:03.325
I did it to myself.

40:03.326 --> 40:04.916
That's a hard thing to admit.

40:06.545 --> 40:07.689
Yeah.

40:08.660 --> 40:09.886
Thank you.

40:09.887 --> 40:12.701
♪ 'Cause the bridge that
burns took you out of the way ♪

