I just think it's a really
cool opportunity, you know?

40:15.241 --> 40:16.601
I mean, how many people get the chance

40:16.602 --> 40:18.031
to have their own TV show?

40:18.900 --> 40:20.363
You know, with Gunnar moving out,

40:20.364 --> 40:22.345
it's like we'd be
starting our life together.

40:22.346 --> 40:23.458
I just think that...

40:23.459 --> 40:24.788
yeah, okay. I'm in.

40:25.620 --> 40:27.197
- You're in?
